In this experiment there will be 4 blocks.
In this task, you will hear a sequence of syllables with different pitches, a pause, then another sequence with different pitches.
Your task is to determine whether the SYLLABLEs/PITCHes in the first sequence are in the same or different order than the SYLLABLEs/PITCHes in the second sequence.
After hearing these two sequences, you will be prompted to indicate whether these sequences are the "same" or "different".
Press "Next" to enter the block.
Remeber to attend PITCHes. Press "Next" to start trials.
Remeber to attend SYLLABLEs (WORDS). Press "Next" to start trials.
